---
title: 'Dill-icious' Cheesy Golden Crusted Chicken  with Bacon-Wrapped Asparagus and Pickle Dip
description: Break out the checkered blanket and wicker baskets — tonight's dinner pays homage to a picnic classic: pickle-brined fried chicken. Finger-friendly sides like roasted potatoes and crunchy veggies make this the shareable feast of your dreams!
